cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.SI, cs.MM, cs.CY

This paper focuses on the detection of devious ad content in Android apps, which falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR). The paper also involves the development of a framework for automated detection, which could be considered as software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SI). The use of automated app testing and ad view exploration strategy involves multimedia (cs.MM) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
